{"word":"G2127 - εὐλογέω - eulogéō - yoo-log-eh'-o - Bless","slug":"G2127","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐλογέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>eulogéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yoo-log-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bless"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - eulogeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>yoo-log-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G3056\">G3056</a>; to <i>speak well of</i>, that is, (religiously) to <i>bless</i> (<i>thank</i> or <i>invoke a benediction upon</i>, <i>prosper</i>): - bless, praise."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1757\">G1757</a>, <a href=\"#/G2128\">G2128</a>, <a href=\"#/G2129\">G2129</a>"}]}